<section id="contact">
  <div class="inner">
    <div class="cinfo rvl">
      <div class="slabel">Get In Touch</div>
      <h2 class="stitle">Let's Build Something <em>Secure</em></h2>
      <p>Ready to secure your infrastructure and accelerate your IT strategy? Our team is on standby to discuss your needs and propose the right solution.</p>
      <div class="citems">
        <div class="citem"><div class="cico">📞</div><div><strong>Phone</strong><span>+254 739 293 691</span></div></div>
