</section>

<footer>
  <div class="ftop">
    <div class="fbrand">
      <div class="logo"><div class="logo-mark"><span>JL</span></div><div style="margin-left:14px"><div class="logo-name">Joshlee Solutions</div><div class="logo-sub">Africa</div></div></div>
      <p>Developing solutions for the future. Nairobi's premier IT consultancy serving enterprises across East Africa and beyond.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="fcol"><h4>Services</h4><ul><li><a href="#services">Cybersecurity</a></li><li><a href="#services">Cloud Security</a></li><li><a href="#services">Network Audit</a></li><li><a href="#services">Software Audit</a></li><li><a href="#services">Turnkey Solutions</a></li></ul></div>
